                <p>This year, 1953, E. T. &amp; H. K. Ide, Inc. celebrates its 140<sup>th</sup> Anniversary in the grain and milling business. It is one of the few companies in this country to have survived for so long a period ... and one of the very few to have been owned and operated continuously for five generations by members of the same family.</p>
