        <p>"Yes," said the boy, "I know the miller always has fat hogs."</p>
        <p>"Well, well," said the miller, "so that is what you know. Tell me what you don't know."</p>
        <p>Said the boy, "I don't know whose corn it is that fattens them."</p>
